name: TT Speed #1
description:
TT Speed sessions are all about becoming accustomed to the sensations of a TT effort. We aim to spend brief periods just below your current FTP setting with minimal recovery. 



The steady-state nature of these intervals will also introduce you to the feeling of laying down a consistent power. We achieve an excellent TT volume by completing the workload at shorter intervals with minimal fatigue.
